Based on a Mexican format, 'Devious Maids' follows four maids with ambition and dreams of their own. They all work for the rich and famous in Beverly Hills. It is all about murder and chaos as the secrets are told. However, Odessa (Melinda Paige Hamilton) does everything to make sure it doesn't happen. Zoila (Judy Reyes) supervises the maids for Genevieve Delatour (Susan Lucci) and works with her daughter, Valentina (Edy Ganem). Little does Zoila know, Valentina has a crush on Genevieve's son, Remi (Drew Van Acker).
